            Our team deploys rapid response units to rescue survivors, provide medical aid, and offer temporary shelter.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    
      <br><hr><br>

      <!-- Landslides -->
      <div class="event">
        <img src="landslide.jpg" alt="Landslide">
        <div class="event-details">
          <h2>Landslides</h2>
          <p>
            We ensure road clearance, assist in relocation, and deliver essential supplies to stranded populations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <br><hr><br>
    
