        <img src="floods.jpeg" alt="Flood">
        <div class="event-details">
          <h2>Floods</h2>
          <p>
            We monitor water levels, distribute relief packages, and support rehabilitation initiatives post-disaster.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

